name: Ted Raymond
description: I would love to meet someone who is caring, has a great sense of humor, can carry a conversation and tell a compelling story and have similar but not identical interests because I am always looking to grow and learn new things. she should be focused and driven but have a playful side and be able to laugh at themselves as well as at life, attentive and affectionate but not smothering. A positive person who looks at the half fullness rather than the half emptiness of things. Someone who also has a healthy understanding of who they are and how they fit into the world around them and has given some thought to the life imprint they want to leave on the world around them and moreover the people around them.
